# Astranyx Licensing

## Licenses

This project has separate licenses for its components.

1. Source Code

   All source and executable code (including game logic, engine code, scripts,
   shaders, build tooling, configuration files, and other machine-executable
   components) is licensed under the GNU General Public License v3.0 or later.
   See LICENSE_CODE for the full license text.

   * SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-3.0-or-later

2. Creative Assets

   All art, music, textures, 3D models, narrative content (including story, lore,
   characters, dialogue, world-building, and written text), and other creative
   assets (excluding fonts) are licensed under the Creative Commons
   Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License. See LICENSE_ASSETS for the
   full license text.

   * SPDX-License-Identifier: CC-BY-SA-4.0

3. Fonts

   Font files are licensed under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1. See
   LICENSE_FONTS for the full license text.

   * SPDX-License-Identifier: OFL-1.1

## Contributions and CLA

By submitting a contribution (including code, documentation, assets, or other
materials) to this project, you agree that:

1. Project Licensing

   Your contribution will be included in the project under the same license
   terms as the component you are contributing to, unless explicitly agreed
   otherwise in writing.

2. Contributor License Agreement

   All contributions are subject to the Contributor License Agreement (CLA).
   The CLA grants the Astranyx Owner additional rights, including a perpetual,
   worldwide, royalty-free license to use, modify, distribute, and relicense
   contributions. See CONTRIBUTOR_AGREEMENT for the full text of the CLA.

## Third-Party Dependencies

Third-party dependencies and assets included in this project retain their
original licenses and are governed by their respective terms.
